name: mdg-opendevelopment
notes: The project goal is to establish an open development business model. Using open data gathered through mobile health applications and organisations working in the field the project will build build an open data repository. Using a Lean feedback loop the the project will test the project assumptions and learn where value can be added and which open data services are sustainable
